Package framework.interfaces

Package containing the interfaces describing additional functionality for your DisplayableObjects.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Animation
    Interface to be implemented by all animated objects to be displayed in a Scene
    Input
    Interface for giving an coursework object input handling.
    Lighting
    Interface for giving an coursework object lighting properties.
